import axios from 'axios'; import { Button } from "bootstrap"; function Dashboard() { const [arrayTemp, setArrayTemp] = useState(); const [lastTemp, setLastTemp] = useState(); const Horas = ["00:00", "01:00", "02:00", "03:00", "04:00", "05:00", "06:00", "07:00", "08:00", "09:00", "10:00", "11:00", "12:00", "13:00","14:00","15:00","16:00","17:00","18:00","19:00","20:00","21:00","22:00","23:00","24:00"] const url = "http://localhost:8080/getTempByPool=1&year=2021&month=11&day=1" let cardTemp = ""; var parametro = temperatura; const openSidebar = () => { document.documentElement.classList.toggle("nav-open"); sidebarToggle.current.classList.toggle("toggled"); }; const sidebarToggle = React.useRef(); useEffect(async () => { let tempHoy=[]; await axios.get(url) .then(response=> { for (let index = 0; index < response.data.length; index++) { tempHoy[index] = response.data[index].temp } setArrayTemp(tempHoy); setLastTemp(response.data[response.data.length-1].temp); }) },[]); useEffect(() => { setInterval(() => { let tempHoy=[]; axios.get(url) .then(response=> { for (let index = 0; index < response.data.length; index++) { tempHoy[index] = response.data[index].temp } setArrayTemp(tempHoy); setLastTemp(response.data[response.data.length-1].temp); }) }, 1000*60); }, []); if (lastTemp > 20) { cardTemp= "fas fa-thermometer-three-quarters text-danger" }else{ cardTemp= "fas fa-thermometer-three-quarters text-primary" } var dashboardTEMPChart = { data: (canvas) => { return { labels: Horas, datasets: [ { data: arrayTemp, fill: false, borderColor: "#51CACF", backgroundColor: "transparent", pointBorderColor: "#51CACF", pointRadius: 4, pointHoverRadius: 4, pointBorderWidth: 8, tension: 0.4, }, ], }; }, options: { plugins: { legend: { display: false }, }, }, }; return ( <>
